sequenceDiagram
    participant Lemon
    participant Clavis
    participant DB as clavis-db
    participant Redis
    participant OPA as opa

    Lemon->>Clavis: Request applications/roles for authenticated user

    Clavis->>DB: Fetch user + status + checksum
    DB-->>Clavis: User record

    Clavis->>Clavis: Validate activation/suspension/deactivation state
    alt Account invalid
        Clavis-->>Lemon: Access denied
    else Account valid
        Clavis->>Redis: Retrieve cached permissions (key: opa:{userId}:{scriptId})
        alt Permissions found
            Redis-->>Clavis: Cached applications/roles
        else Cache miss
            Clavis->>OPA: Compute permissions
            OPA-->>Clavis: Computed applications/roles
            Clavis->>Redis: Cache permissions (key: opa:{userId}:{scriptId})
        end
        Clavis-->>Lemon: Return applications/roles (Access granted)
    end